; RTL-fidelity co-sim helper (Phase-8-style preview, OPT-IN — not a dune test).
; dump_fp_adder runs the Hardcaml Fp_adder over a stimulus set and dumps its outputs; the
; Verilator harness (fp_adder.cpp, driven by run.sh) replays them through the reference
; po/verilog/src/FPAdder.v and asserts RTL z == port z. The dumper builds under `dune build
; @check` (Verilator-free, so it can't silently rot); the actual cross-check is run.sh.

(executable
 (name dump_fp_adder)
 (libraries risc5 hardcaml))
